metadata.name: Social Butterfly
metadata.description:
She's a Social Butterfly. She's statuesque. She's serving "Body-ody-ody" and is feeling her floral resort-wear fantasy. 
My muse is real life goddess, wearing a sexy gown made with layers of printed chiffon, trimmed in gold metallic piping. The side cut-outs showcase a long, lean waist that she annoyingly doesn't have to work hard to maintain. The voluminous skirt flows elegantly as she walks...no...she glides.
